"Dreamcatcher" tells the story of four young friends who perform a heroic act - 
and are changed forever by the uncanny powers they gain in return. 
Years later, on a hunting trip in the Maine woods, they are overtaken by a blizzard, 
a vicious storm in which something much more ominous moves. 
Challenged to stop an alien force, the friends must first prevent the slaughter of innocent civilians by a military vigilante,
